<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00067</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT GRANTING BENEFITS AND PRIVILEGES TO JUNIOR CITIZENS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to develop comprehensive program of benefits and privileges for children aged Zero (0)
to Twelve (12) or Junior Citizens of the Philippines.

Aims to alleviate every parents’ financial woes by providing their children with benefits and privileges that they can enjoy; and effectively address the concerns of our underprivileged Junior Citizens who play an important role in nation-building.
